        "body": "To everyone involved in this conversation: I apologize for not replying until now. I started working full time and had to move twice in between. In addition, my personal machine's HDD died on me and I hadn't had the time to re-setup everything.\r\n\r\nI reviewed your recommendations, but I will have to consult my supervisor on how to proceed on working in this project, since my current work is on a relevant field/product. I will get back to you as soon as I can.\r\n\r\nIn the meanwhile, we can decide on a way to proceed since [~Jim_Brennan] 's comments do have a solid logic behind them.",
